  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires the Office of Wellness and Resilience to develop, implement, and administer a Medical Debt Acquisition and Forgiveness Program to acquire and forgive outstanding medical debt for residents of the State, subject to the availability of program funds.  Requires a report to the Legislature.  Appropriates funds.  (CD1)"
    }
